==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Remind
<hw>Re*mind"</hw> <pr>(r?-m?nd")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To put
(one) in mind of something; to bring to the remembrance of; to bring to
the notice or consideration of (a person).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>When age itself, which will not be defied, shall begin to arrest,
seize, and <qex>remind</qex> us of our mortality.</q>
<rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reminder</ent>⟦br⟧
